Package com.jme.bullet.collision

Class CollisionFlag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jme.bullet.collision.CollisionFlag
  • public class CollisionFlag
extends java.lang.Object
    Named collision flags for a PhysicsCollisionObject. Values must agree with those in BulletCollision/CollisionDispatch/btCollisionObject.h
    Author:
    Stephen Gold sgold@sonic.net
    See Also:
